Sensors
--
tank water level
water flow
ph (ufire probe)
ec (ufire K1 probe)
solution temperature (ufire DS18B20)
dht room
--

Pumps
--
recirculation
irrigation
refill

-(peristaltic)
ph -
nutrient a
nutrient b
nutrient c
--

Additional components
--
heater resistance
reverse osmosis system
solenoids
--

Controllers
--
Siemens SIMATIC S7-1212C (interfacing additional components, water level, flow, dht and photodetector sensors + peristaltic pumps) (*)
Siemens SM-1222 RLY expansion module (interfacing lights, fans, recirculation/irrigation/refill pumps) (*)
ESP8266 (interfacing ph/ec/orp sensors)
--

Panels
--
HMI SIMATIC KTP400 (*)
--

Logic
--
Raspberry PI (o.s. rasbian + home assistant + node red + mosquitto MQTT broker compiled with websockets support) handling automations and scheduled tasks
--

Infrastructure
--
Mosquitto MQTT broker on rpi
MQTT client on ESP8266
MQTT client on S7-1212C
Mikrotik hAP lite


(*) SIMATIC components could be replaced by cheaper sensors/relays boards implementing MQTT protocol. 
    The HMI panel that provides user interface can also be replaced by a tablet targeting a web page or a dedicated app (implementing MQTT)
